* ADC bursts: negligible
* RTC + DPPI: <1 ¬µA
* MCU sleep: ~1‚Äì2 ¬µA

‚û°Ô∏è **Total ‚âà 5‚Äì6 ¬µA**
Very reasonable for a BLE keyboard.
(for 72 switches, a 4000mah battery will last over a year)
